OL,6,FThey say they weren't given the chance
OL,7,Fto change their medication and their
OL,8,Fconcerns were dismissed by doctors and
OL,9,Fother medical experts.
OL,11,FNone of them have told their stories
OL,12,Fbefore - but they say they can now no
OL,13,Flonger stay silent amid institutional
OL,14,Ffailures and unacceptable delays in
OL,15,Ftheir fight for justice.
