OL,6,FCarole McNeil now lives in
OL,7,FBournemouth. Her daughter Sarah was
OL,8,Fborn in 1989 and is now aged 35. She
OL,9,Fhas mobility problems, speech
OL,10,Fdifficulties and learning
OL,11,Fdifficulties. She also had to have an
OL,12,Foperation for scoliosis when she was
OL,13,F14.
OL,15,FCarole had been on sodium valproate
OL,16,Fsince the age of two. She was
OL,17,Fconcerned about taking the medication
OL,18,Fwhile she was pregnant.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/16
