OL,4,Cled to birth defects feel 'abandoned'
OL,6,F"I asked if there was any side effects
OL,7,Fand was told no, you'll be fine," she
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,FShe says she was initially told by
OL,11,Fdoctors that Sarah was double jointed
OL,12,F- but later on a five year battle
OL,13,Fshowed she had sodium valproate
OL,14,Fsyndrome.
OL,16,FShe's angry that information about the
OL,17,Fdrug wasn't shared with patients
OL,18,Fearlier.
OL,20,F"Why, why didn't they tell us?"
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/16
