OL,6,F"The government that knew in 1973 that
OL,7,Fthere was the problem with this drug
OL,8,Fand Sarah was born in 1989, 16 years
OL,9,Fafter.
OL,11,F"It's not right. It's not right."
OL,13,FAn estimated 20,000 children have been
OL,14,Faffected by sodium valproate damage -
OL,15,Fwhich is twice the number in the
OL,16,FThalidomide scandal, a drug that also
OL,17,Fcaused birth defects.
