OL,6,FShe says the government needs to take
OL,7,Furgent action to help families.
OL,9,F"I feel very alone and abandoned," she
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"I feel forgotten. I need things put
OL,13,Fin place for my son. I'm 56 years old."
OL,15,FPenny from Aylesbury in
OL,16,FBuckinghamshire, believes that three
OL,17,Fmiscarriages that she suffered, are
OL,18,Falso a result of the medication. One
OL,19,Fhappened at 16 weeks.
