OL,6,FShe added she was denied the chance to
OL,7,Fmake choices.
OL,9,F"I feel that I could have had the
OL,10,Fmedication changed so easily because
OL,11,Fmy epilepsy was not severe. In fact, I
OL,12,Fdon't know medication now. I haven't
OL,13,Fbeen on medication since 2002."
OL,15,FParents including Jo Gamblin from
OL,16,FFareham in Hampshire say they've been
OL,17,Flet down by the system.
