OL,6,F"This wasn't his fault. It's not my
OL,7,Ffault. And what they seem to be
OL,8,Fforgetting is that we were given the
OL,9,Fmedication to help us in the first
OL,10,Fplace because we've got an illness
OL,11,Fthat is life threatening and now we've
OL,12,Fgot more stress. And stress is one of
OL,13,Fthe biggest triggers for epilepsy."
OL,15,FWell over a year ago a major report
OL,16,Fthat set out how a redress scheme for
OL,17,Fsodium valproate should work was
OL,18,Fpublished.
