OL,6,FWritten by the Patient Safety
OL,7,FCommissioner, Professor Henrietta
OL,8,FHughes, it said there was a "clear
OL,9,Fcase for redress based on the
OL,10,Fsystematic healthcare and regulatory
OL,11,Ffailures".
OL,13,FSixteen months on, there has been no
OL,14,Fresponse from the government, which
OL,15,Fshe describes as "disappointing".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/16
