OL,6,F"The responsibility of all government
OL,7,Fshould be to keep their citizens safe
OL,8,Fand in this situation I believe
OL,9,Fpatients and families have been let
OL,10,Fdown by a system that hasn't focused
OL,11,Fon safety," she said. "The disjointed
OL,12,Fand dismissive nature of the health
OL,13,Fsystem is what led to those patients
OL,14,Fbeing harmed."
OL,16,FThe Department for Health and Social
OL,17,FCare said they would provide an update
OL,18,F"at the earliest opportunity".
