OL,7,Fan incredibly complex issue that
OL,8,Finvolves many different parties
OL,9,Fincluding government, regulators,
OL,10,Fdoctors and other prescribers,
OL,11,Fpharmacists, manufacturers, patients
OL,12,Fand other people affected.
OL,14,F"All partners in the healthcare
OL,15,Fsystem, including health authorities,
